{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Hello, my name is Thomas Heatherwick."},{"time":3000,"text":"I have a studio in London"},{"time":6000,"text":"that has a particular approach"},{"time":8000,"text":"to designing buildings."},{"time":10000,"text":"When I was growing up,"},{"time":12000,"text":"I was exposed to making"},{"time":15000,"text":"and crafts and materials"},{"time":18000,"text":"and invention on a small scale."},{"time":20000,"text":"And I was there looking"},{"time":22000,"text":"at the larger scale of buildings"},{"time":24000,"text":"and finding"},{"time":26000,"text":"that the buildings that were around me"},{"time":28000,"text":"and that were being designed"},{"time":31000,"text":"and that were there in the publications I was seeing"},{"time":35000,"text":"felt soulless and cold."},{"time":38000,"text":"And there on the smaller scale,"},{"time":40000,"text":"the scale of an earring"},{"time":42000,"text":"or a ceramic pot"},{"time":44000,"text":"or a musical instrument,"},{"time":46000,"text":"was a materiality and a soulfulness."},{"time":49000,"text":"And this influenced me."},{"time":53000,"text":"The first building I built was 20 years ago."},{"time":56000,"text":"And since, in the last 20 years,"},{"time":58000,"text":"I've developed a studio in London."},{"time":60000,"text":"Sorry, this was my mother, by the way,"},{"time":62000,"text":"in her bead shop in London."},{"time":64000,"text":"I spent a lot of time counting beads and things like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67000,"text":"I'm just going to show, for people who don't know my studio's work,"},{"time":70000,"text":"a few projects that we've worked on."},{"time":73000,"text":"This is a hospital building."},{"time":77000,"text":"This is a shop for a bag company."},{"time":82000,"text":"This is studios for artists."},{"time":87000,"text":"This is a sculpture"},{"time":89000,"text":"made from a million yards of wire"},{"time":91000,"text":"and 150,000 glass beads"},{"time":93000,"text":"the size of a golf ball."},{"time":96000,"text":"And this is a window display."},{"time":101000,"text":"And this is pair of cooling towers"},{"time":103000,"text":"for an electricity substation"},{"time":105000,"text":"next to St. Paul's Cathedral in London."},{"time":108000,"text":"And this is a temple in Japan"},{"time":110000,"text":"for a Buddhist monk."},{"time":114000,"text":"And this is a cafe by the sea"},{"time":116000,"text":"in Britain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"And just very quickly,"},{"time":120000,"text":"something we've been working on very recently"},{"time":122000,"text":"is we were commissioned by the mayor of London"},{"time":124000,"text":"to design a new bus"},{"time":126000,"text":"that gave the passenger"},{"time":129000,"text":"their freedom again."},{"time":131000,"text":"Because the original Routemaster bus"},{"time":133000,"text":"that some of you may be familiar with,"},{"time":135000,"text":"which had this open platform at the back --"},{"time":137000,"text":"in fact, I think all our Routemasters"},{"time":139000,"text":"are here in California now actually."},{"time":141000,"text":"But they aren't in London."},{"time":144000,"text":"And so you're stuck on a bus."},{"time":146000,"text":"And if the bus is going to stop"},{"time":149000,"text":"and it's three yards away from the bus stop,"},{"time":152000,"text":"you're just a prisoner."},{"time":154000,"text":"But the mayor of London wanted to reintroduce"},{"time":156000,"text":"buses with this open platform."},{"time":159000,"text":"So we've been working with Transport for London,"},{"time":163000,"text":"and that organization"},{"time":165000,"text":"hasn't actually been responsible"},{"time":167000,"text":"as a client for a new bus"},{"time":169000,"text":"for 50 years."},{"time":171000,"text":"And so we've been very lucky to have a chance to work."},{"time":174000,"text":"The brief is that the bus should use 40 percent less energy."},{"time":177000,"text":"So it's got hybrid drive."},{"time":179000,"text":"And we've been working"},{"time":181000,"text":"to try to improve"},{"time":183000,"text":"everything from the fabric"},{"time":185000,"text":"to the format"},{"time":187000,"text":"and structure"},{"time":189000,"text":"and aesthetics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191000,"text":"I was going to show four main projects."},{"time":194000,"text":"And this is a project for a bridge."},{"time":197000,"text":"And so we were commissioned to design a bridge that would open."},{"time":200000,"text":"And openings seemed --"},{"time":202000,"text":"everyone loves opening bridges,"},{"time":204000,"text":"but it's quite a basic thing."},{"time":207000,"text":"I think we all kind of stand and watch."},{"time":209000,"text":"But the bridges that we saw"},{"time":211000,"text":"that opened and closed --"},{"time":214000,"text":"I'm slightly squeamish --"},{"time":218000,"text":"but I once saw a photograph of a footballer"},{"time":221000,"text":"who was diving for a ball."},{"time":223000,"text":"And as he was diving, someone had stamped on his knee,"},{"time":226000,"text":"and it had broken like this."},{"time":229000,"text":"And then we looked at these kinds of bridges"},{"time":233000,"text":"and just couldn't help feeling"},{"time":235000,"text":"that it was a beautiful thing that had broken."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238000,"text":"And so this is in Paddington in London."},{"time":241000,"text":"And it's a very boring bridge, as you can see."},{"time":243000,"text":"It's just steel and timber."},{"time":249000,"text":"But instead of what it is,"},{"time":252000,"text":"our focus was on the way it worked."},{"time":260000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":267000,"text":"So we liked the idea that the two farthest bits of it"},{"time":270000,"text":"would end up kissing each other."},{"time":275000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":283000,"text":"We actually had to halve its speed,"},{"time":285000,"text":"because everyone was too scared when we first did it."},{"time":287000,"text":"So that's it speeded up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289000,"text":"A project that we've been working on very recently"},{"time":292000,"text":"is to design a new biomass power station --"},{"time":295000,"text":"so a power station that uses organic waste material."},{"time":299000,"text":"In the news,"},{"time":301000,"text":"the subject of where our future water is going to come from"},{"time":303000,"text":"and where our power is going to come from"},{"time":305000,"text":"is in all the papers all the time."},{"time":308000,"text":"And we used to be quite proud of the way we generated power."},{"time":312000,"text":"But recently,"},{"time":314000,"text":"any annual report of a power company"},{"time":317000,"text":"doesn't have a power station on it."},{"time":319000,"text":"It has a child running through a field, or something like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"And so when a consortium of engineers approached us"},{"time":327000,"text":"and asked us to work with them on this power station,"},{"time":330000,"text":"our condition was that we would work with them"},{"time":332000,"text":"and that, whatever we did,"},{"time":334000,"text":"we were not just going to decorate a normal power station."},{"time":339000,"text":"And instead, we had to learn -- we kind of forced them to teach us."},{"time":342000,"text":"And so we spent time traveling with them"},{"time":345000,"text":"and learning about all the different elements,"},{"time":347000,"text":"and finding that there were plenty of inefficiencies"},{"time":349000,"text":"that weren't being capitalized on."},{"time":351000,"text":"That just taking a field and banging all these things out"},{"time":354000,"text":"isn't necessarily the most efficient way that they could work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357000,"text":"So we looked at how we could compose all those elements --"},{"time":362000,"text":"instead of just litter, create one composition."},{"time":365000,"text":"And what we found --"},{"time":367000,"text":"this area is one of the poorest parts of Britain."},{"time":369000,"text":"It was voted the worst place in Britain to live."},{"time":372000,"text":"And there are 2,000 new homes being built"},{"time":374000,"text":"next to this power station."},{"time":376000,"text":"So it felt this has a social dimension."},{"time":379000,"text":"It has a symbolic importance."},{"time":381000,"text":"And we should be proud of where our power is coming from,"},{"time":384000,"text":"rather than something we are necessarily ashamed of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387000,"text":"So we were looking at how we could make a power station,"},{"time":389000,"text":"that, instead of keeping people out"},{"time":391000,"text":"and having a big fence around the outside,"},{"time":393000,"text":"could be a place that pulls you in."},{"time":395000,"text":"And it has to be --"},{"time":398000,"text":"I'm trying to get my --"},{"time":400000,"text":"250 feet high."},{"time":403000,"text":"So it felt that what we could try to do"},{"time":406000,"text":"is make a power park"},{"time":408000,"text":"and actually bring the whole area in,"},{"time":410000,"text":"and using the spare soil that's there on the site,"},{"time":413000,"text":"we could make a power station that was silent as well."},{"time":415000,"text":"Because just that soil"},{"time":417000,"text":"could make the acoustic difference."},{"time":419000,"text":"And we also found that we could make a more efficient structure"},{"time":422000,"text":"and have a cost-effective way"},{"time":424000,"text":"of making a structure to do this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426000,"text":"The finished project"},{"time":428000,"text":"is meant to be more than just a power station."},{"time":430000,"text":"It has a space where you could have a bar mitzvah at the top."},{"time":433000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":435000,"text":"And it's a power park."},{"time":439000,"text":"So people can come and really experience this"},{"time":441000,"text":"and also look out all around the area,"},{"time":444000,"text":"and use that height that we have to have for its function."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447000,"text":"In Shanghai,"},{"time":449000,"text":"we were invited to build --"},{"time":451000,"text":"well we weren't invited; what am I talking about."},{"time":453000,"text":"We won the competition, and it was painful to get there."},{"time":456000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":460000,"text":"So we won the competition to build the U.K. pavilion."},{"time":463000,"text":"And an expo"},{"time":465000,"text":"is a totally bonkers thing."},{"time":467000,"text":"There's 250 pavilions."},{"time":470000,"text":"It's the world's biggest ever expo that had ever happened."},{"time":474000,"text":"So there are up to a million people there everyday."},{"time":477000,"text":"And 250 countries all competing."},{"time":479000,"text":"And the British government saying,"},{"time":481000,"text":"\"You need to be in the top five.\""},{"time":483000,"text":"And so that became"},{"time":485000,"text":"the governmental goal --"},{"time":488000,"text":"is, how do you stand out in this chaos,"},{"time":491000,"text":"which is an expo of stimulus?"},{"time":495000,"text":"So our sense was we had to do one thing,"},{"time":499000,"text":"and only one thing,"},{"time":502000,"text":"instead of trying to have everything."},{"time":504000,"text":"And so what we also felt"},{"time":506000,"text":"was that whatever we did we couldn't do a cheesy advert for Britain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":511000,"text":"But the thing that was true,"},{"time":513000,"text":"the expo was about the future of cities,"},{"time":515000,"text":"and particularly the Victorians"},{"time":517000,"text":"pioneered integrating nature into the cities."},{"time":520000,"text":"And the world's first public park of modern times"},{"time":522000,"text":"was in Britain."},{"time":524000,"text":"And the world's first major botanical institution"},{"time":527000,"text":"is in London,"},{"time":529000,"text":"and they have this extraordinary project"},{"time":531000,"text":"where they've been collecting 25 percent"},{"time":533000,"text":"of all the world's plant species."},{"time":535000,"text":"So we suddenly realized that there was this thing."},{"time":538000,"text":"And everyone agrees that trees are beautiful,"},{"time":541000,"text":"and I've never met anyone who says, \"I don't like trees.\""},{"time":543000,"text":"And the same with flowers."},{"time":545000,"text":"I've never met anyone who says, \"I don't like flowers.\""},{"time":548000,"text":"But we realized that seeds --"},{"time":550000,"text":"there's been this very serious project happening --"},{"time":552000,"text":"but that seeds --"},{"time":554000,"text":"at these major botanical gardens,"},{"time":556000,"text":"seeds aren't on show."},{"time":558000,"text":"But you just have to go to a garden center,"},{"time":560000,"text":"and they're in little paper packets."},{"time":562000,"text":"But this phenomenal project's been happening."},{"time":565000,"text":"So we realized we had to make a project"},{"time":567000,"text":"that would be seeds, some kind of seed cathedral."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570000,"text":"But how could we show these teeny-weeny things?"},{"time":573000,"text":"And the film \"Jurassic Park\" actually really helped us."},{"time":576000,"text":"Because the DNA of the dinosaur that was trapped in the amber"},{"time":579000,"text":"gave us some kind of clue"},{"time":582000,"text":"that these tiny things"},{"time":584000,"text":"could be trapped and be made to seem precious,"},{"time":586000,"text":"rather than looking like nuts."},{"time":589000,"text":"So the challenge was,"},{"time":591000,"text":"how are we going to bring light and expose these things?"},{"time":594000,"text":"We didn't want to make a separate building and have separate content."},{"time":597000,"text":"So we were trying to think,"},{"time":599000,"text":"how could we make a whole thing emanate."},{"time":602000,"text":"By the way, we had half the budget of the other Western nations."},{"time":604000,"text":"So that was also in the mix"},{"time":607000,"text":"with the site the size of a football pitch."},{"time":609000,"text":"And so there was one particular toy that gave us a clue."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612000,"text":"(Video) Voice Over: The new Play-Doh Mop Top Hair Shop."},{"time":615000,"text":"Song: ♫ We've got the Mop Tops, the Play-Doh Mop Tops ♫"},{"time":618000,"text":"♫ Just turn the chair and grow Play-Doh hair ♫"},{"time":620000,"text":"♫ They're the Mop Tops ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":622000,"text":"Thomas Heatherwick: Okay, you get the idea."},{"time":624000,"text":"So the idea"},{"time":626000,"text":"was to take these 66,000 seeds"},{"time":628000,"text":"that they agreed to give us,"},{"time":630000,"text":"and to take each seed and trap it"},{"time":632000,"text":"in this precious optical hair"},{"time":635000,"text":"and grow that through this box,"},{"time":638000,"text":"very simple box element,"},{"time":640000,"text":"and make it a building"},{"time":643000,"text":"that could move in the wind."},{"time":645000,"text":"So the whole thing can gently move when the wind blows."},{"time":648000,"text":"And inside, the daylight --"},{"time":650000,"text":"each one is an optic"},{"time":652000,"text":"and it brings light into the center."},{"time":654000,"text":"And by night,"},{"time":656000,"text":"artificial light in each one"},{"time":658000,"text":"emanates and comes out to the outside."},{"time":660000,"text":"And to make the project affordable,"},{"time":663000,"text":"we focused our energy."},{"time":665000,"text":"Instead of building a building as big as the football pitch,"},{"time":667000,"text":"we focused it on this one element."},{"time":670000,"text":"And the government agreed to do that"},{"time":673000,"text":"and not do anything else,"},{"time":675000,"text":"and focus our energy on that."},{"time":677000,"text":"And so the rest of the site was a public space."},{"time":680000,"text":"And with a million people there a day,"},{"time":682000,"text":"it just felt like offering some public space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":685000,"text":"We worked with an AstroTurf manufacturer"},{"time":688000,"text":"to develop a mini-me version"},{"time":690000,"text":"of the seed cathedral,"},{"time":692000,"text":"so that, even if you're partially-sighted,"},{"time":694000,"text":"that it was kind of crunchy and soft,"},{"time":697000,"text":"that piece of landscape that you see there."},{"time":700000,"text":"And then, you know when a pet has an operation"},{"time":704000,"text":"and they shave a bit of the skin"},{"time":706000,"text":"and get rid of the fur --"},{"time":708000,"text":"in order to get you to go into the seed cathedral,"},{"time":711000,"text":"in effect, we've shaved it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713000,"text":"And inside there's nothing;"},{"time":715000,"text":"there's no famous actor's voice;"},{"time":717000,"text":"there's no projections;"},{"time":719000,"text":"there's no televisions; there's no color changing."},{"time":721000,"text":"There's just silence"},{"time":723000,"text":"and a cool temperature."},{"time":726000,"text":"And if a cloud goes past,"},{"time":728000,"text":"you can see a cloud on the tips"},{"time":730000,"text":"where it's letting the light through."},{"time":736000,"text":"This is the only project that we've done"},{"time":738000,"text":"where the finished thing"},{"time":740000,"text":"looked more like a rendering than our renderings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":743000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":749000,"text":"A key thing was how people would interact."},{"time":752000,"text":"I mean, in a way it was the most serious thing"},{"time":754000,"text":"you could possible do at the expo."},{"time":756000,"text":"And I just wanted to show you."},{"time":758000,"text":"The British government --"},{"time":760000,"text":"any government is potentially the worst client in the world"},{"time":763000,"text":"you could ever possibly want to have."},{"time":766000,"text":"And there was a lot of terror."},{"time":769000,"text":"But there was an underlying support."},{"time":772000,"text":"And so there was a moment"},{"time":775000,"text":"when suddenly -- actually, the next thing."},{"time":777000,"text":"This is the head of U.K. Trade and Investment,"},{"time":780000,"text":"who was our client,"},{"time":783000,"text":"with the Chinese children, using the landscape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787000,"text":"(Video) Children: One, two, three, go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":797000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":799000,"text":"TH: I'm sorry about my stupid voice there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":803000,"text":"So finally, texture is something."},{"time":806000,"text":"In the projects we've been working on,"},{"time":809000,"text":"these slick buildings,"},{"time":811000,"text":"where they might be a fancy shape,"},{"time":814000,"text":"but the materiality feels the same,"},{"time":816000,"text":"is something that we've been trying to research really,"},{"time":820000,"text":"and explore alternatives."},{"time":823000,"text":"And the project that we're building in Malaysia"},{"time":826000,"text":"is apartment buildings"},{"time":828000,"text":"for a property developer."},{"time":830000,"text":"And it's in a piece of land"},{"time":832000,"text":"that's this site."},{"time":834000,"text":"And the mayor of Kuala Lumpur"},{"time":836000,"text":"said that, if this developer"},{"time":838000,"text":"would give something that gave something back to the city,"},{"time":841000,"text":"they would give them more gross floor area, buildable."},{"time":844000,"text":"So there was an incentive for the developer"},{"time":846000,"text":"to really try to think about"},{"time":848000,"text":"what would be better for the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":850000,"text":"And the conventional thing with apartment buildings"},{"time":852000,"text":"in this part of the world"},{"time":854000,"text":"is you have your tower,"},{"time":856000,"text":"and you squeeze a few trees around the edge,"},{"time":859000,"text":"and you see cars parked."},{"time":861000,"text":"It's actually only the first couple of floors that you really experience,"},{"time":864000,"text":"and the rest of it is just for postcards."},{"time":867000,"text":"The lowest value is actually the bottom part of a tower like this."},{"time":870000,"text":"So if we could chop that away"},{"time":872000,"text":"and give the building a small bottom,"},{"time":874000,"text":"we could take that bit and put it at the top"},{"time":877000,"text":"where the greater commercial value is for a property developer."},{"time":880000,"text":"And by linking these together,"},{"time":882000,"text":"we could have 90 percent of the site"},{"time":885000,"text":"as a rainforest,"},{"time":887000,"text":"instead of only 10 percent of scrubby trees"},{"time":889000,"text":"and bits of road around buildings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":891000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":895000,"text":"So we're building these buildings."},{"time":898000,"text":"They're actually identical, so it's quite cost-effective."},{"time":901000,"text":"They're just chopped at different heights."},{"time":903000,"text":"But the key part"},{"time":905000,"text":"is trying to give back an extraordinary piece of landscape,"},{"time":908000,"text":"rather than engulf it."},{"time":913000,"text":"And that's my final slide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":916000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":918000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":920000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":922000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":932000,"text":"June Cohen: So thank you. Thank you, Thomas. You're a delight."},{"time":934000,"text":"Since we have an extra minute here,"},{"time":937000,"text":"I thought perhaps you could tell us a little bit about these seeds,"},{"time":940000,"text":"which maybe came from the shaved bit of the building."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944000,"text":"TH: These are a few of the tests we did"},{"time":946000,"text":"when we were building the structure."},{"time":948000,"text":"So there were 66,000 of these."},{"time":951000,"text":"This optic"},{"time":953000,"text":"was 22 feet long."},{"time":955000,"text":"And so the daylight was just coming --"},{"time":958000,"text":"it was caught on the outside of the box"},{"time":961000,"text":"and was coming down to illuminate each seed."},{"time":964000,"text":"Waterproofing the building was a bit crazy."},{"time":967000,"text":"Because it's quite hard to waterproof buildings anyway,"},{"time":970000,"text":"but if you say you're going to drill 66,000 holes in it --"},{"time":974000,"text":"we had quite a time."},{"time":979000,"text":"There was one person in the contractors who was the right size --"},{"time":981000,"text":"and it wasn't a child --"},{"time":983000,"text":"who could fit between them"},{"time":985000,"text":"for the final waterproofing of the building."}]},{"cues":[{"time":987000,"text":"JC: Thank you, Thomas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":989000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}